千巌山
<br/>


<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_svZrBWdHSTrnz6IZKVvsX1_ritxNae4Pbpitl6cjZKLV77TKbo5Vmed_DnnpwCkuY2m7-hEC5-2otpag7HvrjZ1QDY5l3qzMr8xiJjZ1XqwJ4_zLoL383S4Yh53cGZrct2MzwocDgbGjQjFI6uxc992VcY0UOLGu76n0l63_oo18W3EdQ=s0-d"/>
<br/>


我们在展望台吃饭后，就继续下一步行程，先去熊本県立天草青年之家买水，然后到千元森嶽。
<br/>


就在展望台没多远，有个儿童公园，我当时看到很长的滑梯有点发狂，放下包就爬上去玩了。谁料，准备画下来享受刺激一刻时是滑不动的，摩擦力太大了.....
<br/>


<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_uW81BFuULugHcnGpDGuog9Ub04saCTqvSlGn1VlvgsCNcyQMHUjKsDcz6LmgPGv5UwdwcQC-cPs1O7sV6Xw9FeWtwj-LoyhZdbfQT-P8qxyM25IzizD07rov98GzPyzWC-KjpRW-Cn4TO6PyNnuSnqQ-Oack_JwEB-mF5fPQFbobVZ_A=s0-d"/>
<br/>


<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_tecbmwOOvNRfNyPi1H_rZCHegOJ4epUMCKGG4VezCZJA7u0wsYSg814isZcItp0i06iQSxnYP9atbB2qbJ3Gusqe8s4l5JVM1pMoHx-UnefBERPqk5fSZ9nDwDNoJK5pul9Mkj5LTx9cbntNdwlAALcBGFhHGJf0MtWYRIR6ZnOtsJy6o=s0-d"/>
