一家较高级的西餐厅<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_ukw1WT7WExilO3CuNj5-1FNgwci0SlD9W8FzHuJn_LYoIwz0cbb770l5ja6H31T4aBF1nlRgQCwjafXESZPXrNXto8cf9o0CCfTDpGUDMNqThWA431sOUmLm9ePRAN5yVPJ4eDDMF8iuPdJ0DDrC-AuaYCm4YwX2Va8ulsJn6PDfhYOUM=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vDwR-yrOVMmkoNq96LzpDt4sI_TMhZ6ZrFiX-fb_J4tsqDijd-dgmm5FA23f-x-kI_QSKVkZrdTxa1E94eQrJ6_51iM2Tmb2jJCyp_j87HPGatfyKKUrNQH2yVzmKP8iIF7f0RFdwAgzZdOFvQAf2UX14EQgyYwNSiwqmr-_eQS7XoPg=s0-d"/><br/>

上次我在京都游记写过，日本人把紫苏这个简单的东西发挥到极致，到处都是紫苏，被轰炸过后几个月我还没忘记，下次回家我会在淘宝买紫苏叶用来煮紫苏水。这次被轰炸的是天草盐<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vIdwaEqOyhYR3oavQj74YlFw94FZPNvbLLtguxmiq5DILouQ9e-hH7uXORnmRz-QgVl0N4vLCV9cUtRu3R1szFLmslrUeIQkqqsBPIG_uOaI9ea2e-HbYL28smsriK07kQo_DV8NRVaoZ6Z8hvdiznuCm187M-VUaYwJcXzziMNNH7Jg=s0-d"/><br/>

面包护肤品各种食品都有天草盐，搞到我最后买了个天草盐小面包来试，正好当时也饿。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_tjl3NZOQ2wrEKF03JmjkebxMcsegMzlcAqabIgVx9c2WSQr3nwlSoipj-2tImMxgV9oNFRoBbpJgrTHulzHGgziRYcsANMWbiTFaWZn2VKye66D03MHksaOGqb21hFoJWBKFvUPpcuo6mEM88OO-9TMiidF-74myriTbVGa5UBakOAjcw=s0-d"/><br/>

晚饭的时候烤虾带盐，我还刻意的多尝了几口。<br/>

这次再次令我见识日本，味道不怎么样的东西想吸引人买就要靠包装，普通的东西经过不同方面连番轰炸也能吸引人买。<br/>

我逛了这里的礼品店，那些吃的都是带海鲜，果然天草特色。熊在熊本随处可见，这里也是。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vztpQddd3c4dA_tpVdH4nl2J0QHA2BPWFmUL4EOuOhPI_R67R4Xnm8en9dNB4zgwB3rXD9_933sE_85qPTFZj_UkSsXe7DpBQc94Sd3rRa3GRjmN_HBYne3cZ0mNlVvoSZ9wNEb4pMohLii_T-g2pa_2JiiqjqyslwT4xzEoQSodmwJg=s0-d"/><br/>

