吃完我们九点半就出发去sea cruise了，行李可以存在他们的办公室。先去办公室领门票（报上名字就可以)，然后就过去码头准备了。<br/>

船程总共2小时，先开40分钟到A区，之后停留约半小时，再原路往返，期间导游会介绍沿途风景的。<br/>

这个船有厕所，但没饮料卖，自己带好水。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vWS53_YTGZenX7YgsQRn2FrsJTtJU1srHpNfAqa90Bqq0CDwwq4mw49dSiVLPMNIXnCaaIXE0ltft-r46wJjZaYeQz3p9xZ-vGstOTI59bdE4duzL5HHOPSbAVCbAdSYGYeLEqiQ9jTrcMszDES5v3WAL_HJvghPHKyjXvxbod-gU72po=s0-d"/><br/>

这是时刻表<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vjlKRulArJ1vOgcLO-xxPgwipDHaOaYN-cAAIef_xNp0M1XtWoLewW1ID6jniT6H_paFDCdUQIZMyiZhNO_T1VZOhYP72IyN5LCg_rP9W3oDfv-heIBHcpZvxigWrAUmcD2FjDlIze6kDuNiTTGKb1pH470K3eq6Ab6skD200MH-m2uo8=s0-d"/><br/>

下图小船是我们坐的船，又有这个熊，当天只有6名乘客，人多的话会开大船的。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_ufwF-rXYIVK_pjLTQmjO-q7s3hAHvs97dnEPgVgfctaEuaGXTSbVSaLj3uvb6A9AMHk_rv7KIaY1Z-kQyKmuE_V1PPJ4h4nA8VmTWdsEnd5GwrSPfrZmTHCllJ_qkWb1yYfXTNfFvm16_lOLCtoL-ouXdjuPFGeTLXe3aNnIkpRO02QQ=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_v7AJmL19DP8OI7hjSrh7KV6OcePVnlzCNUas8RuYldno6cxIjVk85CK6ybt5Oc7Ry_stHQZUuOzFyZAHFujBLi8hD6PaN3m2dbC1thSYL3YpWEX1C8geJQCwqWBZR-kvEIlHj2bnpXAk5irc0SQvAMNxTKZSHHeCQqaGZTLMbDKj-yTQg=s0-d"/><br/>

这是漂亮可爱的导游mm，会一点点英语。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_umakalKvw0fPDf2DSFcwswMMcEMNX9GzDt5QGOVpGbOFohN6LQMNjJCZ6XVUk24tFQNHXxi6iVkFCu6fQnwUapotR4K2N9F-7Z2lH8jpae_7J_dvlAIi-wb7plg3SDgKJeXQpAf3FKpJ5xXTgnRzPQhavhRni6vJwX3cSBp9YoEU5z-EQ=s0-d"/><br/>

这个小船有室内和室外的位置，我大部分时间都是在外面坐的。外面两排座位，挤一点能坐六人。<br/>

开船了，会先经过天草三条桥。<br/>

下图：五号桥(我们昨天登山夸过的就是这座桥)<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vnGGohrqK6Eb24eh3Cd3Qx76hddpOnzHwV-5XGHl_qNLXHKofANbYlWyotdm6iphb0e8045dIHvmMZ1T1VdAH8C7pq3IJ5J8CEj59JLkEwR9HJlySGuKGDUNoYXhUCpyMEWCP5YGZ3dtX4Ab3WwUxeX1DAMEl-3Umzz86-qs3QoWWa9A=s0-d"/><br/>

下图：三号桥<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_sF4VDjtxUobs1RxFG9nEYxwe7Ru2vMrMxHqLoYme00fvrwiIKeVBi1WR29PyLivgYfuRrR1C18DPjj6ALtjSlnXFNX8Sr3Gu51gXKyD0Gt-wLUdDB1yYcoMOF27Z8DrvCZXaBPOnevColDluoAfwQE9Eiyb-jF32_G0wa21436KUS_Ag=s0-d"/><br/>

下图：四号桥<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_v61Otyt-uvn-W8Kyd0X8nFU2WD1FEjpqUYXNFRyor2LA427tKOJzRYc40eGEWAOnxXrrmskLglohYgmlnRllp7aav2EmgZ8tmNteQgVHxFPgA8Row9XYWhH7ieHrAFehCSuN8TivsfQSGH7v3YcPMsfbyEF6sK7ImHbbFDsy98LpoC1_g=s0-d"/><br/>

没多久就会到天草富士山，天草五桥就是用这里的石头做的。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_uu1qeKn_p26tZPyDyjGriGHgiRsf9V71_6spKlQi3Bz-w9Kl6G4r59z_KDvx8KkjBbAo_uI_uKavNQK8ZrQq8k_X2q5Pg4YJ1o6jglrDeZ3NW3p9LgaOXwbwQe6OxhveUmYuIj4h5ZlkGWegPSKcaHgcash8Yb6XVlzYZoKwGpxXKlnQs=s0-d"/><br/>
<br/>

浪花的亲托下天草富士山更美。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_tIKaccOJTeG1rfdWUYrdMcC66M1tzcGi3sJXwJ2T_aeLpZiiFLLFL4YdpD-3v1ixEvMXxD5JXml-_974aWDLh-W3ahPr3CkV70tccSUBsmigIkVnW2sOs1DQKIfgtWQLb01tWdD4FQvLaQ5VFtLlX-QVSH90qshaHVlbU8SdummyxpNMM=s0-d"/><br/>

之后会经过这个小岛，原来这里还发生过革命的呢。这么小的岛竟然还有人住。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_vRxCmd-rGDp10lmiOYHSp6vG1vmpAC5XSPpmwyelB22hL0lLr10cO59wOKEqIc-mw0KOEFZJWyXms-r0Jttz__wsUDG_J2B2PyP3RdVfol2g0XC7zOz-d6tlbHxv-n99WU1pAo9urrbB_PzGNWfayATIa5Roz-Cb5DYZlFXtvjZVny1wE=s0-d"/><br/>
<br/>

这条船一路晃的很，容易晕船的必定会晕船。即使到了看海豚去听定后也会很晃，拿稳相机拍照。<br/>

好了，到了海豚区了，这里据说有200条海豚，它们一会儿在这个地方出来，出现一两分钟，之后潜水（我看它们潜水时游得很快），然后一会儿又在另一个地方冒出来。我不知道我们看的是不是都是同一批海豚。<br/>

我觉得我们每次看的有大概二三十条吧。它们都朝同一方向游，偶尔会整条跳出来条的很高。<br/>

看海豚的地方对面就是长崎，两边有船往返的。<br/>

上照片。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_tyEsWdFE5i8rh4sEypUoI4hRuWcVIIOhFnfPsNCh7Jlmk6uOJbgka9Vwrm9qGdP7Ph-9JW8kUBDeNxKTdB9RXLYBML3_HC037AG-hCmb-UV0AcEZ6dr_sH-0vzSa6ztQ4kPf7IYwte-8jZKA6QTYf_msAwGNYkMZYT-3mconRQB1lpdaQ=s0-d"/><br/>
