那里出现海豚，船就会驶过去的。这个区域也有其他的海豚游船。<br/>

看海豚真是很好玩，不过时间到了就要回去。回去时天放晴了，上照片。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_sxvT-KDlp0MMQTv_mgKidbUBdU2EcBx3rvfduBAuR_r5garCL-c6ipwvP-DQ_mprosCp9o5v-EFMXq11_cCPD9x0NKY1hawmya21SJvRietZfoUaP-5IKKTtCjB6lyHFRUauwsnt-taRrxFbAUtNHahJ9QOBugEunK_IhEfhZgpLzM2IA=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_uzzAQ63RBBB-lL8yo7Wk28ZKJ-VNdRkQONgKsEuJQNoZl5IUEAgIzLv1DSrJE7R9kmoIw_a_XLRymnxk5Go_SGxNigLErd-32uRL440u42xNguCPeMh3KBxRZxjsbA9MFyrcBbrMEAAOfzOViGIqeV6XjW_uYP8BgGYSRbJ_zopS2d0Q=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_ufkbPMGUShKS2NK7faPtlwavbGulemKFNFIy9spOmPaeRVJ2TDnyycO0mmp8YKFV4P1vsN5cPkn8Fjtz931WqJaGq_VErWzGcKF1BK8Z1AjJaAE2yzxUPS2sDf1LRjuYePfRheomHbit4UL-svRbE6Q5taPYVCXGapAe9Baoe_CXWZpRI=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_sJGvJ12wiNe72OiAksKortavR_-IpPusddeCWJ9bFPN1QfUvr-XLNP54N24zk-dpQVh-b4bK_pM76fUAqbtfye8HqgL9dJhVoe5Tx4pAS_gZRgdUodmkswPJf3OxklP0ldUoanF4kvFH9pIa09bfJkWnV4UI1H5b8aIw8_HizazJIMW1E=s0-d"/><br/>

十二点准时到码头，去领完行李后我们就往南走几百米到潮まねき再吃一次海鲜餐。这里有高级的海鲜餐，要预定。<br/>

我吃的海鲜当，rgg吃的海鲜定食，生鱼片和昨天的差不多，最有意思是我们的虾和昨天的反过来，今天我吃熟的，他吃生的。这只生虾人家已经把壳剥掉，而且虾肠也挑了出来，不过虾还是动的.....感觉好像活吞那样。人家技术真是高，昨晚我把虾拿在手里，它就挣脱出来，最后要强行去头。（两个套餐都是1580日元，另外加税）<br/>

我们的午餐：<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_thcttd4SETBxIkRytE4El7vV7_uABd5kst5ZcpC4Cf9nIUOCyNwYSoATAMyFhaDmuqNMngUCXmDP2aWU7x-UMlSeggO_9HLi0IkXd2taz77FVB8S2ttpaG9auytjqudI0kImEoo3_EnqjLpxOOZKpSAsRCBVTdHYIolokq1sHnHw_T7k0=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_tv5GP-yOyfxSwYCU3iZUzlJxemqAOTiwvwvlb-SatvJCwTqXdfYOKfMvohxRz7IXSK-leAHatWDxvI3YikIChc9a1b8Wc_GFIJu1xL3R0KNfE8UyP6XLRu3Kk9W26rUadJ0A1g2-Z7m266XuZn4oNQg8wBE-gJMNVogkO7YW1XGBi7sOA=s0-d"/><br/>

这里环境也是很棒的，向海，有室内和室外位置。<br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_tUGfsIkeA3q050qshtdZEmJlgaYhBw1FBFQHPxyWCiKKuN0-X_FS85IKfzMTgLCxjD8jQSDNXdar314FX9wpFex4cg8W0Ki0fmZV4CTTNyUvqS1sos0pmy8CIg_AU67dh31vu_nuHC0DohTUhIMUGoI7Ii10Eg43x6DIdcGQsAsAHACw=s0-d"/><br/>
<img class="replace-file-img" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blogger_img_proxy/AEn0k_uSppVhZ0pvp3Qu8I6NNw_E45t4vZqUk1WzW1L31MDsAPMAR5H_GwCMJCC2Ikz7kQjYvafLBViWK4UXeNZCctvkjukqFSkYmSPPGUlJg66ABql3XEbJLw5-TUXvAmGudhVMr4W6yvduO3Y2EdVIyxV31fz2Ilzc__kBiIqxIaLmfdQDaSg=s0-d"/><br/>
